{"tid":2401831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唐英傑案不設陪審團 張達明：理據薄弱、不合常理 湯家驊：迫不得已","createTime":"2021-02-10T04:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:24:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"144af3adfe4aaa471eaa2e6e7cbd95a6193f7a11","tid":2401831,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"有法律界消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，律政司決定，首宗《港區國安法》案件「唐英傑案」將不設陪審團。港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，今次律政司以陪審團安全作為原因，理據較薄弱、不合常理，但認為「咩理由都好，佢都會搵辦法，唔會有陪審員嫁啦」。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊則形容決定是「迫不得已」，相信以陪審團審理政治化、高敏感度案件的機會不高。<br />\n<br />\n張達明在商台節目上表示，當《國安法》中有不需陪審團審理的條文，「已經知佢一定唔會俾陪審團審」、「唔會放心交俾香港市民決定係咪要執行國安法」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今次律政司以陪審團安全作為原因，張達明認為理據較薄弱、不合常理，指中央官員已肯定《國安法》後，香港已「止暴制亂」，危險相信不是來自抗爭者的陣營，反問「唔通佢判咗無罪，反而安危會有影響？唔會係咁掛」。<br />\n<br />\n他預計，律政司不需要在法庭上就決定給予具體及詳細解釋，可以司法覆核的空間亦狹窄，但就不肯定法庭在處理此問題時，會根據普通法的原則處理，抑或在《國安法》下有不同做法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%82%91%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%A8%AD%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98-%E5%BC%B5%E9%81%94%E6%98%8E-%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%E8%96%84%E5%BC%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E5%B8%B8%E7%90%86-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E8%BF%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B7%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%259C%2598-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2598%258E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%2596%2584%25E5%25BC%25B1-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%2590%2586-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25B7%25B2%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=6b014069\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%259C%2598-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2598%258E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%2596%2584%25E5%25BC%25B1-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%2590%2586-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25B7%25B2%2F&h=469039d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%82%91%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%A8%AD%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%9C%98-%E5%BC%B5%E9%81%94%E6%98%8E-%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%E8%96%84%E5%BC%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E5%B8%B8%E7%90%86-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E8%BF%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B7%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"96605934cada72fcd232aa07ec9bbfddfe6c7795","tid":2401831,"uid":59633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"判左無罪既話，班陪審團先危險呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e804d2d1d286fbda3c8ed37edbdf4bd5d50d8d","tid":2401831,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"迫不得已食幻幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95975038ef97926ce7b032faa188e1d9674c780","tid":2401831,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96605934cada72fcd232aa07ec9bbfddfe6c7795","tid":2401831,"uid":59633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"判左無罪既話，班陪審團先危險呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多人仲信陪審團係公平公正地抽出？"},{"pid":"71560ad98fe8f019d8e4470509080df5c911d8bb","tid":2401831,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"想判幾多年咪判lo<br />\n扮乜撚野"},{"pid":"c89d26572ff67be00ca4f7b9d525caf1d61fc248","tid":2401831,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d95975038ef97926ce7b032faa188e1d9674c780","tid":2401831,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96605934cada72fcd232aa07ec9bbfddfe6c7795","tid":2401831,"uid":59633,"like":6,"